, 2011/qc-e}}\n\n==2008 - 40th general election==\n{{Canadian federal election, 2008/qc-e}}\n\n==2006 - 39th general election==\n{{Canadian federal election, 2006/qc-e}}\n\n==2004 - 38th general election==\n{{Canadian federal election, 2004/qc-e}}\n=== Maps ===\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-break}}\n#Gasp\u00e9sie-\u00celes-de-la-Madeleine\n#L\u00e9vis-Bellechasse\n#Matap\u00e9dia-Matane\n#Rimouski-T\u00e9miscouata\n#Rivi\u00e8re-du-Loup-Montmagny\n{{col-break}}\n<gallery widths=185 heights=185>\neq04.PNG|Key map\neqbq.PNG|Bloc Qu\u00e9b\u00e9cois\neqcpc.PNG|Conservative Party of Canada\neqgpc.PNG|Green Party of Canada\neqlpc.PNG|Liberal Party of Canada\neqndp.PNG|New Democratic Party\n</gallery>\n{{col-end}}\n\n==2000 - 37th general election==\n{{Canadian federal election, 2000/qc-e}}\n\n== 1997 - 36th general election ==\n{{Canadian politics/candlist header|province=CA|BQ|Liberal|PC|NDP|Other}}\n|-\n| style=\"background-color:whitesmoke\" |[[Bellechasse\u2014Etchemins\u2014Montmagny\u2014L'Islet|Bellechasse\u2014Etchemins\u2014Montmagny\u2014L'Islet]]\n|\n|[[Fran\u00e7ois Langlois]]<br>14,053\n|{{Canadian party colour|CA|Liberal|background}}|\n|[[Gilbert Normand]]<br>14,100\n|\n|Denis Roy<br>12,840\n|\n|Branda Michaud<br>520\n|\n|Ga\u00e9tan Pouliot (<small>[[Reform Party of Canada|Reform]]</small>)<br>611\n|{{Canadian party colour|CA|BQ|background}}|\n|Fran\u00e7ois Langlois<br><small>''[[Bellechasse (electoral district)|Bellechasse]]''</small>\n|-\n| rowspan=3 style=\"background-color:whitesmoke\" |[[Bonaventure\u2014Gasp\u00e9\u2014\u00celes-de-la-Madeleine\u2014Pabok|Bonaventure\u2014Gasp\u00e9\u2014\u00celes-de-la-Madeleine\u2014Pabok]]\n|rowspan=3 {{Canadian party colour|CA|BQ|background}}|\n|rowspan=3|[[Yvan Bernier]]<br>15,983\n|rowspan=3|\n|rowspan=3|[[Patrick Gagnon]]<br>15,804\n|rowspan=3|\n|rowspan=3|Yves Quinton<br>6,297\n|rowspan=3|\n|rowspan=3|Dennis P. Drainville<br>649\n|rowspan=3|\n|rowspan=3|\n|{{Canadian party colour|CA|Liberal|background}}|\n|Patrick 